body: "Documentation plan:\n- docs/QUICKSTART.md: mention pm init guidance behavior and the explicit later-add option.\n- docs/AGENT_GUIDE.md: describe that AGENTS.md/CLAUDE.md should contain bootstrap/orient/claim/link/verify/close basics and that pm init can add a compact block.\n- docs/COMMANDS.md: add init option examples and clarify non-interactive behavior.\n- src/cli/guide-topics.ts / guide-shell docs if needed: route agents to this workflow without requiring full README context.\n- plugins/pm-claude/commands/pm-init.md and plugins/pm-codex README/commands if relevant: keep harness-specific startup guidance aligned with the new core behavior.\n- Avoid duplicating the entire AGENTS.md content; link or summarize core commands only."
